data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom ranch home close to restaurants, shopping, and the Falling waters Trail.  Beautiful hardwood floors through most of the home, gas fireplace in the living room, with tons of natural light coming through the front windows, along with an updated bathroom.  There is a second bathroom in the basement, along with room to add additional living space. Fenced in yard with a 2 car garage.  Bring your paint and furniture and move in and make it your dream home.
